Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit digital marketplace floating in a dark cyber void, with towering holographic storefronts shaped like glowing app icons competing for attention. Two distinct robotic figures stand on opposing platforms—one sleek and consumer-friendly, the other bulky and industrial with corporate aesthetics—facing each other in a tense standoff. Between them, streams of data packets and digital applications flow like rivers of light, caught in the crossfire. The scene is bathed in electric blues, hot pinks, and amber oranges, with rain streaking through the neon glow. Circuit board patterns and binary code cascade like waterfalls in the background, while small drone-like devices hover around carrying miniature software packages. The atmosphere crackles with competitive energy and technological tension.
